{"title":"Flexbox布局","date":"2020-02-11T13:43:37.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Feb 11, 2020","L":"02/11/2020","MM-DD":"02-11"},"link":"post/Web/CSS/Flexbox布局","categories":["CSS","Web"],"updated":"2020-02-11T14:08:12.398Z","content":"<h1 id=\"结构\">结构<a href=\"#结构\" title=\"结构\"></a></h1><img src=\"/post/Web/CSS/Flexbox%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80/1.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<h1 id=\"container属性\">Container属性<a href=\"#container属性\" title=\"Container属性\"></a></h1><h2 id=\"display\">display<a href=\"#display\" title=\"display\"></a></h2><p>指定布局为flexbox布局。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.container</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">display</span>: flex;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"flex-direction\">flex-direction<a href=\"#flex-direction\" title=\"flex-direction\"></a></h2><p>指定item排布的顺序。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.container</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">flex-direction</span>: row | row-reverse | column | column-reverse;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><strong>row</strong></p>\n<p>从左到右。默认。</p>\n<img src=\"/post/Web/CSS/Flexbox%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80/2.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<p><strong>row-reverse</strong></p>\n<p>从右到左。</p>\n<img src=\"/post/Web/CSS/Flexbox%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80/3.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<p><strong>column</strong></p>\n<p>从上到下。</p>\n<img src=\"/post/Web/CSS/Flexbox%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80/4.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<p><strong>column-reverse</strong></p>\n<p>从下到上。</p>\n<img src=\"/post/Web/CSS/Flexbox%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80/5.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<h2 id=\"flex-wrap\">flex-wrap<a href=\"#flex-wrap\" title=\"flex-wrap\"></a></h2><p>指定如何换行。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.container</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">flex-wrap</span>: nowrap | wrap | wrap-reverse;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><strong>nowrap</strong></p>\n<p>不换行。默认</p>\n<img src=\"/post/Web/CSS/Flexbox%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80/6.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<p><strong>wrap</strong></p>\n<p>换行，新的一行在下面。</p>\n<img src=\"/post/Web/CSS/Flexbox%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80/7.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<p><strong>wrap-reverse</strong></p>\n<img src=\"/post/Web/CSS/Flexbox%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80/8.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<p>换行，新的一行在上面。</p>\n<h2 id=\"justify-content\">justify-content<a href=\"#justify-content\" title=\"justify-content\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.container</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">justify-content</span>: flex-start | flex-end | center | space-between | space-around | space-evenly | start | end | left | right ... + safe | unsafe;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>指定行内item在水平方向上如何排布。</p>\n<img src=\"/post/Web/CSS/Flexbox%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80/9.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<p><strong>space-around</strong></p>\n<p>弹性盒子元素会平均地分布在行里，两端保留子元素与子元素之间间距大小的一半。</p>\n<p><strong>space-evenly</strong></p>\n<p>弹性盒子元素会平均地分布在行里，没两个子元素间的距离都一样。</p>\n<h2 id=\"align-items\">align-items<a href=\"#align-items\" title=\"align-items\"></a></h2><p>指定行内item在垂直方向上如何排布。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.container</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">align-items</span>: stretch | flex-start | flex-end | center | baseline | first baseline | last baseline | start | end | self-start | self-end + ... safe | unsafe;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<img src=\"/post/Web/CSS/Flexbox%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80/10.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<h2 id=\"align-content\">align-content<a href=\"#align-content\" title=\"align-content\"></a></h2><p>指定不同行之间如何排布。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.container</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">align-content</span>: flex-start | flex-end | center | space-between | space-around | space-evenly | stretch | start | end | baseline | first baseline | last baseline + ... safe | unsafe;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<img src=\"/post/Web/CSS/Flexbox%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80/11.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<h1 id=\"item属性\">Item属性<a href=\"#item属性\" title=\"Item属性\"></a></h1><h2 id=\"order\">order<a href=\"#order\" title=\"order\"></a></h2><p>用于指定子元素排布在行内的顺序。数值小的排在前面，可以为负值。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.item</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">order</span>: &lt;integer&gt;; <span class=\"comment\">/* default is 0 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"flex-grow\">flex-grow<a href=\"#flex-grow\" title=\"flex-grow\"></a></h2><p>TODO</p>\n<h2 id=\"flex-shrink\">flex-shrink<a href=\"#flex-shrink\" title=\"flex-shrink\"></a></h2><p>TODO</p>\n<h2 id=\"flex-basis\">flex-basis<a href=\"#flex-basis\" title=\"flex-basis\"></a></h2><p>TODO</p>\n<h2 id=\"align-self\">align-self<a href=\"#align-self\" title=\"align-self\"></a></h2><p>用于覆盖父容器指定的align-items。</p>\n<h1 id=\"参考文档\">参考文档<a href=\"#参考文档\" title=\"参考文档\"></a></h1><ol><li><p><a href=\"https://css-tricks.com/snippets/css/a-guide-to-flexbox/#flexbox-background\" target=\"_blank\">A Complete Guide to Flexbox</a></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><a href=\"http://caibaojian.com/flexbox-guide.html\" target=\"_blank\">Flexbox布局详解</a></p>\n</li>\n</ol>","prev":{"title":"4-SQL优化之排查方法","link":"post/数据库/MySQL/4-SQL优化之排查方法"},"next":{"title":"3-SQL优化之Explain","link":"post/数据库/MySQL/3-SQL优化之Explain"},"plink":"https://beginc.github.io/post/Web/CSS/Flexbox布局/","toc":[{"id":"结构","title":"结构","index":"1"},{"id":"container属性","title":"Container属性","index":"2","children":[{"id":"display","title":"display","index":"2.1"},{"id":"flex-direction","title":"flex-direction","index":"2.2"},{"id":"flex-wrap","title":"flex-wrap","index":"2.3"},{"id":"justify-content","title":"justify-content","index":"2.4"},{"id":"align-items","title":"align-items","index":"2.5"},{"id":"align-content","title":"align-content","index":"2.6"}]},{"id":"item属性","title":"Item属性","index":"3","children":[{"id":"order","title":"order","index":"3.1"},{"id":"flex-grow","title":"flex-grow","index":"3.2"},{"id":"flex-shrink","title":"flex-shrink","index":"3.3"},{"id":"flex-basis","title":"flex-basis","index":"3.4"},{"id":"align-self","title":"align-self","index":"3.5"}]},{"id":"参考文档","title":"参考文档","index":"4"}]}